fields.Title: ICE / ACELE AND ASSOCIATES
fields.Description: this is where the "ask about acele's associates" and "what's your name" branches are located.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Tore it to pieces.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Tore it to pieces."

fields.Title: You: ""What does he do?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What does he do?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""What do you want to know?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What do you want to know?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""What do you mean?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What do you mean?"

fields.Title: You: ""Tell me about the others.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Tell me about the others."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Unfortunately, I can confirm that.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Unfortunately, I can confirm that."

fields.Title: You: ""Actually, no.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Actually, no."

fields.Title: Acele: ""One time we were out partying, som..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "One time we were out partying, somewhere in backwater Faubourg. Or maybe even Coal City, I can't remember. Maybe it was Coal City..."

fields.Title: Acele: ""He abides by the hard core, sir. Y..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "He abides by the hard core, sir. You would have to ask him yourself."

fields.Title: You: ""What kind of mindset is that?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What kind of mindset is that?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""It means I don't answer questions..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It means I don't answer questions about myself."

fields.Title: You: ""No offence taken, go on.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "No offence taken, go on."

fields.Title: You: ""Actually, do tell me about *yourse..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Actually, do tell me about *yourself*."

fields.Title: You: ""What is this pilgrimage you're tal..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What is this pilgrimage you're talking about?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""I've never seen him so psyched abo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I've never seen him so psyched about anything though -- and he's often psyched. Looked sort of desperate, like it's his last chance or something. Or maybe he was just high..."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Okay, then you should go and take..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay, then you should go and take a look, I guess. Boogie Street is cool. It's got a lot of immigrants and all kinds of different people."

fields.Title: You: ""Tell me more about him.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Tell me more about him."

fields.Title: You: ""There's more to you than you let o..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "There's more to you than you let on. What am I not seeing?"

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "A strange feeling... Every now and..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A strange feeling... Every now and then, something feels off about the way she speaks. She doesn't change tone, but you feel as though there's more about her than she lets on.

fields.Title: You: ""And your surname?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "And your surname?"

fields.Title: You: ""What does he do up there?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What does he do up there?"

fields.Title: You: ""Yes, I forgot. Tell me about yours..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes, I forgot. Tell me about yourself."

fields.Title: Acele: ""I mean, not that he does drugs. Ju..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I mean, not that he does drugs. Just *high* you know."

fields.Title: Jump to: [Acele: ""Who do you want to know about?""]
You: ""Yes.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Acele.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Acele."

fields.Title: You: ""Tell me about Soona.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Tell me about Soona."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Okay.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay."
fields.Alternate1: "Sure. You helped us out, I can repay the favour. What do you want to know?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""What do you want to know?" She smi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What do you want to know?" She smiles a little.

fields.Title: Acele: ""It was definitely Coal City, becau..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It was definitely Coal City, because it took us two days to walk back to the Fau. He just wheezed the whole way, we never really asked him why he came with us. Or who he was. I think his name is Germaine..."

fields.Title: You: ""Tell me about the others.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Tell me about the others."

fields.Title: You: ""No, I meant for breakfast. Of cour..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "No, I meant for breakfast. Of course for a living."

fields.Title: You: ""Is that because of his beliefs? Th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Is that because of his beliefs? The hard core and the ribs, the... spinal cord and stuff?"
fields.Alternate1: "That's because Noid is violently hard core. I have internalized it. I understand why he doesn't stoop to servitude. Do you?"

fields.Title: Jump to: [Acele: ""What do you want to know?""]
Reaction Speed: "There's that phrase again. It reall..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There's that phrase again. It really reminds you of... *something*.

fields.Title: Logic: "A very common name."
fields.Dialogue Text: A very common name.

fields.Title: Acele: ""Uh, okay..." She nods."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Uh, okay..." She nods.

fields.Title: Acele: ""Anyway, even if you don't have voc..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Anyway, even if you don't have vocals you still need someone to say something every now and then, right? To urge things on. That's where the party boy comes in..."

fields.Title: You: ""You don't have to tell *me* rock m..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You don't have to tell *me* rock music is dead. I abandoned rock music a long time ago. Can't disco to rock!"
fields.Alternate1: "You don't have to tell *me* rock is backward. I am The Futureman. I abandoned rock in the Thirties. Stupid rock." (Spit.)

fields.Title: Conceptualization: "Ptew ptew! Sweeesh! Your credential..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Ptew ptew! Sweeesh! Your credentials as the resident Futureman of Revachol are being questioned. Show her you're hip with the times, gramps!

fields.Title: Acele: ""He basically just stands on the st..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "He basically just stands on the stage and dances and yells how awesome everything is. It's very catchy."

fields.Title: Acele: ""He's real hard core about the life..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "He's real hard core about the lifestyle."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Beats me... Noid said they get alo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Beats me... Noid said they get along, somehow. They're both crazy enough, I guess."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Come to think of it, yes!" She lau..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Come to think of it, yes!" She laughs.

fields.Title: You: ""Could it be that he's balding? Him..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Could it be that he's balding? Him thinking it's his last chance?"

fields.Title: You: ""What does that mean?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What does that mean?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Anyway..." He looks around, a litt..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Anyway..." He looks around, a little embarrassed of the enthusiasm of his interjection.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""That would depend on the circumsta..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "That would depend on the circumstances." The lieutenant taps his foot.

fields.Title: Acele: ""Sure..." she says, slightly disori..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Sure..." she says, slightly disoriented. "What do you want to know?"

fields.Title: You: ""And you?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "And you?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""Why?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""Oh, the crab-man." She shudders. "..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh, the crab-man." She shudders. "Still gives me the creeps, the way he moves... But he doesn't actually come down that much, just climbs around the rafters."

fields.Title: You: ""Okay, lets leave it at that then.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay, lets leave it at that then."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I understand. People are usually a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I understand. People are usually afraid to do things if others aren't already doing them. Dancing makes you dance like sneezing makes you sneeze. Or yawning makes you..."

fields.Title: Empathy: "You can see it must have been a gre..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You can see it must have been a great night. The memory causes her to go silent for a moment or two.

fields.Title: Acele: ""It's just something poor Faubourg..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's just something poor Faubourg kids do every spring, to pass the time. We walk the entire length of Boogie Street, up to Jamrock. Or as much as possible."

fields.Title: Acele: ""There is.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "There is."

fields.Title: You: ""What do you think of the crab-man?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What do you think of the crab-man?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""Andre? He's a cool guy. Doesn't re..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Andre? He's a cool guy. Doesn't really come off as one, but he is. To me at least..."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Is there a law that would stop me..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Is there a law that would stop me from lying, though?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""I'm a silver bird.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm a silver bird."
fields.Alternate1: "I told you, I'm a silver bird."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Egg was yelling along to some jams..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Egg was yelling along to some jams someone was spinning, all night long. Just kept yelling until he didn't have a shred of voice left. When the sun came up over the mines... there were mines? Yeah, it was in Coal City!" She nods.

fields.Title: You: ""Oh, and I'm also a raging fascist..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh, and I'm also a raging fascist who doesn't approve of *different people* -- so no, I don't think I'll be going."

fields.Title: You: ""Relax, girl. I am a police officer..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Relax, girl. I am a police officer, but I'm perfectly corrupt. You can tell me about drugs and shit, I don't care."
fields.Alternate1: "Relax girl. We're police officers, but we're corrupt, rotten to the marrow. You can tell us about drugs and shit, I don't give fuck."

fields.Title: Acele: ""He's a carpenter. Trained and all...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "He's a carpenter. Trained and all. He's very good, he just doesn't have the mindset to work like that -- in a shop somewhere."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Yeah," she says, then opens her mo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah," she says, then opens her mouth like she's about to add something, but doesn't.
fields.Alternate1: "Yeah," she says, then adds: "I hope you do."

fields.Title: You: ""Acele who? I'm not a young suitor,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Acele who? I'm not a young suitor, this is official police business."

fields.Title: Acele: ""I don't know man, have you *been*..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't know man, have you *been* down Boogie Street? It's a little bewildering."

fields.Title: Perception (Sight): "She rubs her sides, but not from co..."
fields.Dialogue Text: She rubs her sides, but not from cold. Her shoulders are relaxed. She must have taken a hit or she's on an upswing.

fields.Title: Acele: ""He's a Faubourger I guess, like th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "He's a Faubourger I guess, like the rest of us. Okay, maybe not Egg, I don't know about him, but Noid and the rest are from Faubourg, making the pilgrimage up north to visit The Paliseum."

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "This is the first time you've heard..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This is the first time you've heard her laugh.

fields.Title: Acele: ""Yes." She nods studiously. "Foreve..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes." She nods studiously. "Forever..."

fields.Title: You: ""Fair enough.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Fair enough."

fields.Title: Acele: ""People are sweet," she says quietl..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "People are sweet," she says quietly.

fields.Title: Acele: ""They do say death is an avenue. Li..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "They do say death is an avenue. Like all the others." She's silent for a second like she's going to add something. But she doesn't.
fields.Alternate1: "They do say death is an avenue like any other." She's silent for a second. "I still think you'll make it to Boogie Street, though."
fields.Alternate2: "They do say death is an avenue like any other." She's silent for a second. "I still think you'll make it to Boogie Street, though."

fields.Title: You: ""Why indeed? Forget it.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why indeed? Forget it."

fields.Title: Encyclopedia: "The worst of the *banlieues*. A wre..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The worst of the *banlieues*. A wretched heap of closed-down mines even west of Jamrock, on the dusty slope of Mont Martin. The remotest possible area of Revachol, no one even wants to exploit those people anymore.

fields.Title: You: ""Thank you. Some other questions.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Thank you. Some other questions."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Actually, we don't know where he's..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Actually, we don't know where he's from. Or who he is, really."

fields.Title: You: ""Tell me more about Egg.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Tell me more about Egg."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Uh... no?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Uh... no?"
fields.Alternate1: "Uhm... kind of? I'm gonna say: yes."

fields.Title: Perception (Sight): "Her hair is dyed blonde, with dark..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Her hair is dyed blonde, with dark roots showing. There's a coarseness to her features, some masculinity below that timidness.

fields.Title: Jump to: [tellin about dudes hub EGG]
You: ""What's a party boy?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What's a party boy?"
fields.Alternate1: "He told me as much, but what exactly is a party boy?"

fields.Title: You: ""God damn right, rock music is the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "God damn right, rock music is the coolest. Rock music forever!"

fields.Title: Acele: ""What do you mean, 'do'? Like for a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What do you mean, 'do'? Like for a living?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""Sir," she gives you a switchblade..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Sir," she gives you a switchblade smile. "I abide by *the law*."

fields.Title: Acele: ""I just try to stay away from the c..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I just try to stay away from the crab-man, but he talks to Noid. They seem to have some 'thing' going on."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Uh, yes. Anyway.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Uh, yes. Anyway."

fields.Title: You: ""Tore that shit up.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Tore that shit up."

fields.Title: You: ""Is Andre your boyfriend?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Is Andre your boyfriend?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""Okay..." She hesitates. "It's Berg..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay..." She hesitates. "It's Berger."

fields.Title: You: ""I'm from the police. It's for the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm from the police. It's for the paperwork."
fields.Alternate1: "Did I not say I was from the police? It's for the paperwork."

fields.Title: You: ""Why wouldn't it be?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Why wouldn't it be?"

fields.Title: You: ""What's the deal with Egg Head?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What's the deal with Egg Head?"

fields.Title: You: ""What does he think he's doing when..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What does he think he's doing when he yells all that stuff?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""Me?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Me?"

fields.Title: Jump to: [Acele: ""Who do you want to know about?""]
Jump to: [Acele: ""Who do you want to know about?""]
You: ""Actually, tell me about the others.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Actually, tell me about the others."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Must have taken it as a sign when..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Must have taken it as a sign when he found it abandoned like that. Said it was an *augury*. I don't know where he got that from." She smiles. "Andre's not super intelligent..."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Uh... she's a bit odd, I have to s..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Uh... she's a bit odd, I have to say. Doesn't talk much. I'm not really sure how to vibe with her, y'know? Seems like she's not in a very good mood most of the time."

fields.Title: You: ""Oh, I'm sorry... have I not told y..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh, I'm sorry... have I not told you I'm a raging alcoholic who recently drank himself into an oblivion so deep he can't even remember what sounds like the biggest street in the city?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""Who do you want to know about?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Who do you want to know about?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""Yes, better that way...""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes, better that way..."

fields.Title: Empathy: "A quick response. She's very sure o..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A quick response. She's very sure of it. He's someone she feels she can trust and even control, if need be.

fields.Title: Acele: ""But earlier today she told me abou..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "But earlier today she told me about... welkins?" Acele grimaces, as if it's the first time hearing the word. "And she seemed oddly happy. Like she had had some idea with those... little creatures. Some artistic idea. I didn't really listen, I was busy with my mic."

fields.Title: Acele: ""He's in some kind of a self-destru..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "He's in some kind of a self-destruction mode with that hair of his. Bleaching it like that. Probably wants to get rid of it altogether."

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "You wish you'd been there."
fields.Dialogue Text: You wish you'd been there.

fields.Title: Acele: ""He takes care of shit. Sorry, I me..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "He takes care of shit. Sorry, I mean he's got a *vision*. Of what life should be, you know? He tries to push things until everything falls into place. He's an organizer."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Thank you.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Thank you."

fields.Title: You: ""Let's say I *haven't* been down Bo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Let's say I *haven't* been down Boogie Street."

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "A strange feeling... like before, w..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A strange feeling... like before, when you caught her lying better than she should have. Every now and then something feels off about the way she speaks. She doesn't exactly change tone, but you feel as though there's more about her than she lets on.

fields.Title: You: ""Tell me about Andre.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Tell me about Andre."

fields.Title: You: ""Where's he from? How long has he b..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Where's he from? How long has he been with you guys?"

fields.Title: Jump to: [Acele: ""Who do you want to know about?""]
Kim Kitsuragi: ""Yeah. Drugs. Shit. Fuck. We don't..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah. Drugs. Shit. Fuck. We don't care." He smirks.

fields.Title: Acele: ""Wow. You really *have* talked to h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Wow. You really *have* talked to him." She smiles. "Indeed. Noid serves no master but the beat."

fields.Title: You: ""Because I'm not. Now tell me somet..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Because I'm not. Now tell me something else about Noid."

fields.Title: You: ""Well, I am.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Well, I am."

fields.Title: Jump to: [tellin about dudes hub EGG]
Reaction Speed: "Hang on, that phrase. You're sudden..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Hang on, that phrase. You're suddenly reminded of... *something*.

fields.Title: You: ""Tell me about Noid.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Tell me about Noid."

fields.Title: You: ""But I'm a police officer. You *hav..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "But I'm a police officer. You *have* to answer me."

fields.Title: You: ""Tell me about the others.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Tell me about the others."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Egg came with us. He made this whe..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Egg came with us. He made this wheezing puppy dog sound all the way back. Couldn't even speak."

fields.Title: You: ""It's unlikely I'll make it there...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's unlikely I'll make it there. Chest pains. Need to continue drinking. But thank you."

fields.Title: You: ""I might just do that if I make it..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I might just do that if I make it there alive."

fields.Title: You: ""We certainly saw that in practice,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "We certainly saw that in practice, didn't we?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""Nothing. But then again... there's..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Nothing. But then again... there's nothing to organize around here either. He really wants this church thing to work..."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Yes." She nods."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes." She nods.

fields.Title: You: ""Thanks. About the others...""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Thanks. About the others..."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Who knows?" She shrugs. "He doesn'..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Who knows?" She shrugs. "He doesn't really answer our questions, see. Not that it's easy to ask them. What are we supposed to do, yell up at the tower?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""Anodic music doesn't really do voc..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Anodic music doesn't really do vocals in the traditional sense. Vocals are thought of as *rock*. That's to say they're a bit *backward*. No offence if you like rock music, though. Rock music is cool by me."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Yes, I suppose we did.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes, I suppose we did."

fields.Title: Acele: ""Okay." She shrugs. "To each his ow..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay." She shrugs. "To each his own."

fields.Title: Jump to: [tellin about dudes hub EGG]
Acele: ""Not to sound too dramatic, but I w..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Not to sound too dramatic, but I wouldn't make light of his belief system when he's around. Noid's a serious person. He's serious about the lifestyle."

fields.Title: Authority: "You have little reason to doubt tha..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You have little reason to doubt that's her real name, but... she's not all that surprised by this cop-show questioning, is she?

fields.Title: Jump to: [Acele: ""Who do you want to know about?""]
Acele: ""Oh, that... he's the party boy.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh, that... he's the party boy."

fields.Title: You: ""On his mother's love?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "On his mother's love?"

fields.Title: You: ""On life?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "On life?"

fields.Title: You: ""What has he organized?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What has he organized?"

fields.Title: Acele: ""Alright." She picks up the tape re..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Alright." She picks up the tape recorder and looks you in the eye...

fields.Title: Jump to: [tellin about dudes hub EGG]
You: ""Oh, he talks to Noid? What for?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Oh, he talks to Noid? What for?"
